Leroy is a musician from Walla Walla in eastern Washington. Leroy was born on the 19th of February, 1965.[1] Leroy has had two songs that have been featured on the TV series Scrubs, and one on the series Arrested Development. His song ?New World? has been featured on the 10 Things I Hate About You soundtrack.
